---
description: Enforce local formatting checks to match CI (Black + isort).
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Before committing or pushing, run:
  - `python -m black src/ tests/ --line-length=120`
  - `isort src/ tests/ --profile=black`
- For quick validation (CI-style), run:
  - `python -m black --check --diff src/ tests/ --line-length=120`
  - `isort --check-only --diff src/ tests/ --profile=black`
- Keep imports sorted and lines wrapped per Black (120 chars) and isort profile=black.

